lready notice a difference. Well worth it<\/strong><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["heading_4VNRVD","text_7zy7yB"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"center","color_scheme":"scheme-156b13b9-b85d-4aea-b2d5-bc69b8208eff","full_width":true,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"rich_text_L6kMAD":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_9tDFnW":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<a href=\"\/products\/reliefease-joint-massager\" title=\"ULTRA KNEE MASSAGER\">GET <\/a>UP TO 20% OFF NOW","heading_size":"h1"}}},"block_order":["heading_9tDFnW"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"center","color_scheme":"scheme-5d993f92-f4e8-42ad-aebb-a93953a7020f","full_width":true,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"rich_text_nEdKmw":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_KtQ6Tg":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Do You Relate?","heading_size":"h1"}},"text_6pwYzp":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Imagine being able to<strong> relieve your chronic pains, stiffness, swelling<\/strong> <strong>from <\/strong>the comfort of <strong>your home – in just a few minutes<\/strong> – <strong>without <\/strong>taking <strong>painkillers<\/strong> or <strong>expensive  lengthy therapy<\/strong>…<br\/><br\/><strong>There is so much more out there in life<\/strong>, however it requires mobility, no one wants to carry one another. Everyone wants to enjoy the beauty of life and its special moments. It requires moving, <strong>having somthing in which prevents the moving is a big problem.<\/strong><br\/><br\/>Premium Heals isn't just a store for your health, its a team that solved the problem, from what started as issues in all our families to trying everything from A-Z, surgeries, therapy, medication, and so much more. <strong>We lost some important people in our lives. We don't want that for you and your loved ones.<\/strong><\/p><p><strong>It took a while until we found the solutions, trial after trial. Product researches, doctors and so much time. We finally found somthing...<\/strong><\/p><p><strong>For the first time in moderation, your able to heal your problems from the good of your home without the need of<\/strong> taking drugs, spending time for therapy that would throw you if you didn't pay and surgeries that simply put you out for as long as its needed. <br\/><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["heading_KtQ6Tg","text_6pwYzp"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"center","color_scheme":"scheme-156b13b9-b85d-4aea-b2d5-bc69b8208eff","full_width":true,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":52}},"image_with_text_UXR6ib":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_CVhFCL":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"What is it?","heading_size":"h1"}},"text_X6A4Mm":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>The Ultra Knee Massager, is a device that uses 3 combinations in world of healing:<br\/><strong>Heat + Red Light + Movement<br\/><\/strong>These 3 combinations produce an <strong>enhanced healing effect <\/strong>to the knees by reducing inflammation and promoting natural healing, ideal for managing chronic pain. <strong>With this You are able to regenerate your knees and rid off all your pains and be able to move freely and see life for what it is ~ Premium Heals<\/strong><\/p>","text_style":"body"}},"button_zrX8iV":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"GET IT","button_link":"shopify:\/\/products\/ultra-knee-massager","button_style_secondary":false}}},"block_order":["heading_CVhFCL","text_X6A4Mm","button_zrX8iV"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/zzzz_snoring_zzzz.jpg","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"image_first","image_behavior":"none","content_layout":"no-overlap","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignmen